  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Akagawa Jirou - Yasoukyoku 2 is the sequel to Akagawa Jirou - Yasoukyoku, a first person perspective adventure game that was also released later for the Nintendo DS console.\n\nThis adventure game is also adapted from Akagawa Jirou's classic mystery novel Yasoukyoku and this sequel contains three separate detective stories. The stage is set in a Library, a mansion hidden in a small town where a collection of books related to death are stored.",
